@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ilnlpg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v1 - 0.89)
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.00) * (tmp + 0.30 / tmp + 0.63)) / wp.cos(0.10))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.57)) / v0)
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos(0.25))
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
